Package: RepertoireGraphs
Title: Repertoire Graphical Visualization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ido",
           family = "Hasson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "idoh@systemsbiomed.org",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8382-5638"))
Description: Provides visualization options of repertoire datasets
    including comparison of sequence frequency among samples, network of
    similar sequences and convergent recombination source presentation
    between species. Currently repertoire analysis is in early stage
    development, hence new practices for data examination and assessment
    are crucial.
